additionalInfo.description:
This maplet parses a phone number that follows the standard format for the United Kingdom from a string of text into its own field. 
The parsing string can recongize phone numbers with a leading zero or with the +44 international dialing code and phone extensions prefixed with hash(#). 
For best results, remove multiple spaces and any punctuation other than plus(+),parenthesis () or hash (#).

Tags: Great Britian, Company, Customer, Europe, UK, Parse, Phone
